<Link id="l00236" /><CodeLine lineNumber="236"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The following set of template specializations implement GraphTraits to treat</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00237" /><CodeLine lineNumber="237"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// any VPBlockBase as a node in a graph of VPBlockBases. It&#39;s important to note</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00238" /><CodeLine lineNumber="238"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// that VPBlockBase traits don&#39;t recurse into VPRegioBlocks, i.e., if the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00239" /><CodeLine lineNumber="239"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// VPBlockBase is a VPRegionBlock, this specialization provides access to its</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00240" /><CodeLine lineNumber="240"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// successors/predecessors but not to the blocks inside the region.</span></CodeLine>
